records.name: Barceló Nasandhura Malé

descriptions.direction: Located in Malé, Barcelo Nasandhura Male is in the city center and near the beach. Maldives Islamic Centre and Medhu Ziyaaraiy are local landmarks, and the area's natural beauty can be seen at Sultan Park and Rasfannu. Spend some time exploring the area's activities, including whale-watching.
descriptions.general: Overlooking the pristine Maldivian waters, the Barceló Nasandhura Malé harbours a corner of tranquil luxury in the vibrant capital of Maldives.
descriptions.localized: Overlooking the pristine Maldivian waters, the Barceló Nasandhura Malé harbours a corner of tranquil luxury in the vibrant capital of Maldives.
